*********************************
*****
*****  PROGRAMMING IN RUBY  *****
*****
*********************************


For those using Linux, there is a script named "setup-ruby-linux.sh" which will
download various Ruby programming language related documentation to your computer.
It will require Subversion (SVN), Git and Hg (Mercurial) to be installed.


Links:

https://www.ruby-lang.org/en/
http://www.ruby-doc.org/
http://www.rdoc.info/
https://www.ruby-toolbox.com/
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ruby_%28programming_language%29
http://rubyonrails.org/


Books:

ISBN-13: 9780596516178 -- THE RUBY PROGRAMMING LANGUAGE
ISBN-13: 9781937785499 -- PROGRAMMING RUBY 1.9 & 2.0
ISBN-13: 9780596523695 -- RUBY COOKBOOK

